[11:08:37] [33mWARN[39m: [36mPOST /api/issues/4ab94770-5b41-4b78-9717-50b88c5c760b/comments 409[39m [90m{"reqBody":{"body":"## Deployment: /app 301 Redirect Fix\n\n**Status:** Ready for deployment to Hostinger VPS\n\n### Config Change Verified\n- File: `server/nginx-retaileros.conf` lines 88-90\n- Fix: Added `location = /app` with internal rewrite rule\n- Effect: `/app` will return 200 OK instead of 301 redirect\n\n```nginx\nlocation = /app {\n    rewrite ^/app$ /app/ last;\n}\n```\n\n### Deployment Steps (VPS)\n1. SSH into Hostinger VPS\n2. Copy updated config:\n   ```bash\n   cp server/nginx-retaileros.conf /etc/nginx/sites-available/retaileros.in\n   ```\n3. Test nginx syntax:\n   ```bash\n   nginx -t\n   ```\n   Expected: `nginx: configuration file test is successful`\n4. Reload nginx:\n   ```bash\n   systemctl reload nginx\n   ```\n5. Verify fix:\n   ```bash\n   curl -I https://retaileros.in/app\n   curl -I https://retaileros.in/app/\n   ```\n   Both should return 200 OK\n\n### Rollback Plan\nIf deployment causes issues:\n```bash\ngit checkout server/nginx-retaileros.conf\ncp server/nginx-retaileros.conf /etc/nginx/sites-available/retaileros.in\nnginx -t && systemctl reload nginx\n```\n\nAwaiting VPS access to execute deployment."},"routePath":"/issues/:id/comments"}[39m
